data.description: ***$10,000 SELLER CONCESSIONS TO USE ANYWAY YOU WANT! (Closing Costs or Interest Rate Buy Down) *** Welcome to one of the most beautiful homes in the Arcadia Ridge Community! Located at 1920 Artemis Path, this stunning home boast a gorgeous curb appeal with stone and stucco exterior and a huge drive way. Upon entering the home, you will have a large office directly to the left and access to your powder bathroom, laundry/utility room, with your garage access located to the right. After further entry, you will enter the primary living space with second floor high ceilings and tons of windows for natural light. On the right you will notice your open concept kitchen with large granite counter tops, 40 inch white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. To the rear of the home you will find access to your primary bedroom which has bay windows as well as high ceilings. Your primary bathroom has a separate shower-tub combo with a built in shower bench and double vanity sinks with tons of storage below. On the second level you will find your additional 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a large loft, and an enclosed game room. With a huge backyard and covered patio, this home is the perfect place for entertaining guests! Our clients loved this home and we believe you will too! Schedule your tour today to find your new dream home.
